quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  45,22,"God created the heavens and the earth to manifest the Truth, and to recompense each soul according to its deeds. They shall not be wronged"
  45,23,"Do but consider: who, besides God, can guide him who makes his lust his god, whom God deliberately confounds, setting a seal upon his ears and heart, and drawing a veil over his eyes? Will you not take thought"
  45,24,"They say: ‘There is but one life in this world and no other. We die and live; nothing but Time destroys us.‘ Surely of this they have no knowledge. They are merely guessing"
  45,25,"And when Our veritable revelations are recited to them, their only argument is: ‘Bring back our forefathers, if what you say be true!‘"
  45,26,"Say: ‘God it is who gives you life and then causes you to die; He will then gather you all on the Day of Resurrection, of which there is no doubt; yet most do not know it.‘"